name: VR Tower Climbing
summary:
Challenging skyscraper climbing.
Experience the thrill as you climb from one floor of a building to another by utilizing your surroundings as a guide through intricate architecture.
Use our leaderboards to see how fast you can get to the top and compare your performance to your friends.

Features:

Variability: reach the top of the skyscraper using different routes;

Leaderboards: upload your highscores to Oculus Leaderboard and compare them with your friends;
